==English==
===Etymology===
With reference to the golden apple in Greek [[mythology]], inscribed ‘for the fairest female’, which sparked dissent among the gods and led to the judgment of Paris, and ultimately to the Trojan war.

===Noun===
'''[[apple]] [[of]] [[discord]]'''

# an object which sows dissention and anger.

